-- Twitter replaces CFO Mike Gupta with former Goldman executive
-- By Supantha Mukherjee in Bangalore
-- Tue Jul 01, 2014 09:34AM EDT
-- None



July 1 (Reuters) - Twitter Inc <TWTR.N> said Chief Financial Officer Mike Gupta will become senior vice president of strategic investments and named Anthony Noto as his replacement.

Noto, 46, was a managing director in Goldman Sachs' <GS.N> technology, media and telecom investment banking group, Twitter said in a regulatory statement. [ID:nEOL61ZCcm]